    <item>
      <title>特朗普试图利用海伦的回应来吸引北卡罗来纳州的选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-uses-helene-aid-as-wedge-issue-in-appeal-to-storm-victims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普严厉批评了联邦政府对飓风海伦的反应，重复了毫无根据的说法，即救援资金被用在了无证移民身上，而不是飓风受害者身上，因为这位共和党候选人试图在战场北卡罗来纳州争取选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-uses-helene-aid-as-wedge-issue-in-appeal-to-storm-victims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 17:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
